Spotify sdk update, and bug fixes

title: Revert to previous support lib
message:
Revert to previous support lib

Support library versions above 23.0.1 have a bug where nothing but the first item in a row can be selected. Navigation to the next item breaks the selection and nothing can be selected.

title: Filter out x64 native libs
message:
Filter out x64 native libs

The spotify sdk doesn't currently support x64 architectures. x64 android systems can use x32 libs, but for some reason the new gradle plugin does not package the native libs correctly, which causes a crash.
